lenders.occupational_info:
Lithonia Lighting introduces a better lighting experience with an innovative design that is also easy on the pockets – the Reality LED Downlight. The Reality LED downlight was designed as a lighting solution to rising energy costs and increasingly demanding energy codes. With integrated LED lighting technology, the Reality can deliver quality lighting and remarkable energy savings.

To accommodate retrofitting and lighting renovations, the Reality LED is made for easy and quick installation. It fits in most popular six inch housings and can easily replace its incandescent and CFL counterparts. It is also sold with a housing or as a module to fit a wide range of downlighting applications.

The Reality’s LED lights are rated for over 50,000 hours of service which virtually eliminates the need for lamp replacement. It also uses 80% less energy than a standard 65W BR30 lamp, making it a truly cost effective lighting solution. With Reality LED lighting, you can have high-quality and comfortable lighting for your residential, commercial and architectural spaces.

While the usual lighting renovation often stops at lamp replacement (or relamp), more and more people are opting for fixture and system replacements as well or what is now being termed a relight. With a wide range of products that include indoor lighting, outdoor lighting and lighting control systems, we are a perfect resource for your relighting needs.
